SmartFixer Application Download
==============================

To create a proper executable application with icon:

1. Save this file to your computer
2. Extract the ZIP file contents
3. Install PyInstaller: pip install pyinstaller
4. Run: pyinstaller --onefile --windowed --icon=icon.ico SmartFixer-App.py
5. The executable will be in the "dist" folder

For detailed instructions, read "HOW_TO_CREATE_APPLICATION.md"

Requirements:
- Python 3.11 or higher installed on your system

Thank you for using SmartFixer!
